[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     67[0m:[38;5;10m[49m   1. **The therapeutic-content library is a per-content-item versioned governance artifact owned by behavioral-health clinical leadership, with the clinical-leadership's signature as the launch gate per content item.** The architecture should specify per-content-item semantic versioning, sandbox testing against held-out support cases including crisis-adjacent presentations, staged rollout with per-content-item canary, rollback-on-regression, named ownership at behavioral-health clinical leadership plus operations plus compliance plus regulatory team, behavioral-health-clinical-leadership signature as launch gate per content item, annual review cadence with re-signoff, per-content-version stamping on every support-decision-record, indication-and-contraindication tagging discipline, and the per-content change-management process.
